Pedro D. MELENDEZ and Lourdes Marte a/k/a Lourdes Melendez, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEUTSCHE BANK NATIONAL TRUST, AS TRUSTEE FOR J.P. MORGAN MORTGAGE ACQUISITION TRUST 2007-CH4, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3556 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. November 01, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for writ of certiorari is dismissed for petitioner's failure to respond to this court's order of October 17, 2018.

CASANUEVA, SILBERMAN, and CRENSHAW, JJ., Concur.
